title: Install Argocd on Openshift
tags: @zettel _method argocd openshift
roam-id: a6b134a8-d805-49fd-b681-148807d8638c
type: text/markdown

- reference: [Getting Started with ArgoCD on OpenShift 4 - YouTube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xYCX2EejSMc)
- login as **kubeadmin** to your openshift web console
- go to opeartorhub
- search for argocd
- install argocd on a namespace
- after installing
- go to \"installed opeartors\"
- go to \"Argo CD\" tab
- click on \"Crete ArgoCD\"
